VUTYUVACHU RAMU JIRYA: rirvatidye vichasara nijyanvay jmurvasavay,

VUTYUVACHU RAMUNTIY: jiryatiy raniy sitenu vatasara datyadoda jarvedo

VUTYUVACHU RAMUNTIY: jiryatiy ntyuchuma raju mucadi jnutyavay caterava

VUTYUVACHU RAMUNTIY: jirvatiy rtiy jto darva, tiUau nijyanvay
rarvidatyarurva jirva tuchoda;

TITAJU NIJYANVAJYU rirvatidye tuvachu variy ramu. Raniy raryivicha

Ne sarupay nijyami cumudeju darvantyamuy javatyasjiu. Jachipiyadati

TUCHUSARA 6.

Ne ti rarvivichasara jirich1 mityamusiy, darvantyamuy tanuvunujomuju,

TUCHUSARA l0.

TUCHUSARA 11.

2.Text:
Rirvivichaniy juchajsani tuchutasi netimyu ridyityanu vijyomujachera

Ne ti rarvitye ti barvamuyu, ne vinu satevamyu, darvantyamuy sarorimyu,

TUCHUSARA 13.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvirupiñumaya jimyucadiva rirvatidye jarveta variy

TtDau nijyanvay rarvisipyatay tamucadimusiy, darvantya riryichipyatay j

Titaju nijyanvay rarvivicha mucaditavay.
Ne ti rarvijubay mucaditi vichadajisiñL darvantyamuy sjaatyachirva

TUCHUSARA 16.
Jamyiñumatiy vaduy, vatuy jerve, rirvjaamuy variy yisJau nrvatidye jude

Ne ti rarvijamutyaniñi vanu surramusiy, netimyu savatadidrva jamuyada,

Jirvatiy rndesara vutyevay jamuyadamusiy, detuyadamusiy jarve,

TUCHUSARA 17.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvivichasara taratavay, varimyata nuñi timusiy,
varimyata rajumusiy.

Ne ij raryichovay mityamusirya riberya tavay.
TUCHUSARA 18.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvijarveta munatya j ijechipiyjaadamu nutyaramusiy

Saryidityanu datyadodamusiy varirva, daryantya jváyadamusiy, daryantya j

TUCHUSARA 19.
Ne ti raijubaa satiy jachipiya tara, sarvinique varirva jijechipiyjaada.
Darvantyamuy sarvijiyasanta sajachipiyjaadivayu. Vanu rarvijtajanu riva

Sarvidatyanu varirva jijechipiyjaada titjau vichadiva, nutyaramusiñitiy

Titaju nijyanvay rarvijntyeaniy tavatyayu, netimyu rintyrvaniy tj

Ne ti raryijnty£ryanityaniy ijsjaunI satidye jvay tara jasiy rusa.
TUCHUSARA 21.

j iryatiy sajaryeta yibivajunj Vumyucadi jnutityumiy rarvijmutyariy

Ne rirvimurchenu tqui jarvi timusiy darva jvayada murichirva.

Deramiy jamiy raryijaryetasara nutyara catera nJuyomu nrvadatya
ridyedyeñu.
TUCHUSARA 27.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvisityarira jityevay vichada, rirvijchanatyantirya j

samirva fljyu.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvivatara rirvatidye jnuy tavay samirva ranacho

TUCHUSARA 28.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvivata ratidye jdutyara vuvyichada jirya mucadimu,
rirvatidye datyasara t-itDau jiatiy nuchara jiyudarva.

TUCHUSARA 29.
Titaju nijyanvay rarvidivyirva samirva vichada jivyichadamu jirvatiy
vinu rivyichadamu Hrvijavye samirva.
Titjau nijyanvay rarvisaboniy jimyucadi niquejadamuyu rirvatidye

Tama rirvivichasara nijyanvay jirva niquejada jiyarjou jiatiy ntyuchu
raju mucadimusirva.
TUCHUSARA 30.
Ne rirvadatyasara nijyanvarva jirva niquejada rirvatidye javatya ratara

samirva vichada. Ranuma titajura.
